import {
  Box,
  Card,
  CardContent,
  Container,
  FormControl,
  FormControlLabel,
  FormHelperText,
  InputLabel,
  makeStyles,
  TextField,
} from "@material-ui/core"

const useStyles = makeStyles()

const Login = () => {
  return (
    <Container maxWidth="md">
      <Card>
        <CardContent>
          <form>
            <FormControl>
              <TextField
                variant="outlined"
                margin="normal"
                required
                fullWidth
                id="email"
                label="Email Address"
                name="email"
                autoComplete="email"
                autoFocus
              ></TextField>
            </FormControl>
          </form>
        </CardContent>
      </Card>
    </Container>
  )
}

export default Login
